Name: WEAPON TYPE, GENERIC
Explanation: THE CODE THAT CAN BE USED TO IDENTIFY A WEAPON. THIS TABLE SHOULD ONLY BE USED WHERE THERE IS NO SUITABLE WEAPON AVAILABLE IN AN ALTERNATIVE PICK LIST.

Name: SURFACE-TO-AIR WEAPON SYSTEM
Explanation: THE CODE FOR THE ORDNANCE TYPE DESIGNED TO BE FIRED FROM THE SURFACE TO OPERATE AGAINST AN AIRBORNE TARGET ABOVE THE SURFACE.

Name: ORDNANCE WEAPON TYPE, SURFACE-TO-AIR
Explanation: THE CODE FOR THE ORDNANCE TYPE DESIGNED TO BE FIRED FROM THE SURFACE TO OPERATE AGAINST AN AIRBORNE TARGET ABOVE THE SURFACE.

Name: MISSILE TYPE
Explanation: SPECIFIES MISSILE TYPES WITHIN A WEAPON SYSTEM ENVIRONMENT.

Name: ENEMY WEAPONS
Explanation: THE IDENTITY OF THE ENEMY WEAPON, FOR EXAMPLE: "SSN9".

Name: WEAPON TYPE, SHORT RANGE AIR DEFENCE SYSTEM
FIRE UNIT WEAPON TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE SURFACE-TO-SURFACE FIRE SUPPORT WEAPON.

Name: WEAPON SYSTEM ASUW
Explanation: ASUW = ANTI-SURFACE WARFARE.

Name: SURFACE-TO-AIR WEAPON SYSTEM TYPE, OTHER
Explanation: THE TYPE OF SURFACE TO AIR WEAPON.

Name: ORDNANCE WEAPON TYPE, ANTI-SUBSURFACE
Explanation: THE ORDNANCE / WEAPON TYPE FOR ANTI-SUBSURFACE.

Name: MISSILE TYPE, ABBREVIATED
Explanation: THE ABBREVIATED CODE TO INDICATE THE TYPE OF CRUISE MISSILE.

Name: CHAFF FLARE TYPE
Explanation: THE TYPE OF CHAFF AND FLARE.

Name: ORDNANCE WEAPON TYPE, AIR-TO-AIR
Explanation: THE CODE FOR THE ORDNANCE/WEAPON TYPE DESIGNED TO BE FIRED OR RELEASED FROM AN AIRBORNE CARRIER AT AN AIRBORNE TARGET.

Name: ORDNANCE WEAPON TYPE AIR-TO-SURFACE
Explanation: THE CODE FOR THE ORDNANCE/WEAPON TYPE DESIGNED TO BE FIRED OR RELEASED FROM AN AIRBORNE CARRIER TO IMPACT ON THE SURFACE OR A GROUND TARGET.

Name: AREA WEAPON CONTROL SAW
Explanation: THE DETAILS OF THE TACTICAL CONTROL REQUIRED FOR ANY SURFACE-TO-AIR WEAPONS (SAW) UNIT.

Name: ANTI-AIR WARFARE (AAW) WEAPON CATEGORY
Explanation: A CATEGORY DESCRIPTION FOR MARITIME WEAPONS CAPABLE OF BEING USED IN THE ANTI-AIR WARFARE ROLE.

Name: ANTI-SUBMARINE WARFARE (ASW) WEAPON CATEGORY
Explanation: A CATEGORY DESCRIPTION FOR MARITIME WEAPONS CAPABLE OF BEING USED IN THE ANTI-SUBMARINE WARFARE ROLE.

Name: ANTI-SURFACE WARFARE (ASUW) WEAPON CATEGORY
Explanation: A CATEGORY DESCRIPTION FOR MARITIME WEAPONS CAPABLE OF BEING USED IN THE ANTI-SURFACE WARFARE ROLE.

Name: THREAT MISSILE, SPECIFIC
Explanation: A SPECIFIC MODEL OR TYPE OF ANTI-SHIP MISSILE WHICH MAY BE CONSIDERED A POTENTIAL THREAT TO OWN AND/OR FRIENDLY FORCES.

Name: THREAT MISSILE, GENERIC
Explanation: A LITERAL NAME OR DESIGNATOR FOR ANY MODEL OR TYPE OF ANTI-SHIP MISSILE CONSIDERED A POTENTIAL THREAT TO OWN AND/OR FRIENDLY FORCES BUT WHICH IS NOT LISTED UNDER FUD 'THREAT MISSILE, SPECIFIC'.

Name: AIRCRAFT MISSILE TYPE
Explanation: SPECIFIES MISSILE TYPES WITHIN A WEAPON SYSTEM ENVIRONMENT.

Name: ASW HELICOPTER WEAPON TYPE
Explanation: GENERIC WEAPON TYPES THAT CAN BE LOADED ONTO A HELICOPTER FOR AN ASW MISSION.

Name: WEAPON TYPE EXPENDED
Explanation: THE TYPE OF ORDNANCE OR WEAPON EXPENDED ON TASKED TARGET.

Name: MARITIME GUNNERY SYSTEMS
Explanation: A LIST OF GUNNERY SYSTEMS FOR USE WITH MARITIME MESSAGES.

Name: MARITIME UNDERWATER SYSTEMS
Explanation: A LIST OF UNDERWATER WEAPON SYSTEMS FOR USE WITH MARITIME MESSAGES.

Name: MARITIME WEAPON SYSTEMS
Explanation: A LIST OF MARITIME WEAPON SYSTEMS FOR USE WITH MARITIME MESSAGES. THIS TABLE IS A COMBINATION OF GUNNERY, UNDERWATER, AND ABOVE WATER WEAPONS.

Name: MARITIME ABOVE WATER WEAPON SYSTEMS
Explanation: A LIST OF ABOVE WATER WEAPON SYSTEMS FOR USE WITH MARITIME MESSAGES.
